       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI10202.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI10202.
      *
      *     Detalhe de Ausęncia
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI10202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD7601 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3401 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV1020.
       COPY COCV1021.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL1000.
       COPY VIATW300.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT7601 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT7601'.
           05 CON-COVT3401 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3401'.
           05 CON-01       PIC X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-99       PIC X(02) VALUE '99'.
           05 CON-D        PIC X(01) VALUE 'D'.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(01) VALUE 'S'.

       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CONTADOR          PIC 9(04) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA   PIC X(02).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI10202'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT76 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                       CIDEMP
                     , DDATAUS
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , NHORAS
                     , CSITU
                     , CUSERAPR
                     , DDATAPR
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                 FROM COVT7601
                 WHERE   CIDEMP    = :COCD7601-CIDEMP
                    AND  DDATAUS   = :COCD7601-DDATAUS
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI10202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV1020-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1020-ASE               TO COCV1021-ASE.
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-CONTADOR.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1020-ADE       TO COCV1021-ADE.

      *-----------------------------------------*
      *--- Verifica se o periodo está aberto ---*
      *-----------------------------------------*
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1001-VER-PERIODO THRU 1001-VER-PERIODO-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Validar se marcaram férias em fim de semana      ---*
      *--------------------------------------------------------*
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1002-VER-FERIAS  THRU 1002-VER-FERIAS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--------------------------------------------------------*

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 END-IF
              END-IF
              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     1001-VER-PERIODO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1001-VER-PERIODO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1001-VER-PERIODO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV1020-DDATAUS         TO WS-DTMESANO.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO-ANO          TO COCD3401-ZANO.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO-MES          TO COCD3401-ZMES.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT CSITU
                  , CSITUER
               INTO :COCD3401-CSITU
                  , :COCD3401-CSITUER
               FROM COVT3401_PERIODO
            WHERE ZANO     = :COCD3401-ZANO
              AND ZMES     = :COCD3401-ZMES
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3401               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK AND COCD3401-CSITU = COCK0002-SITU-ABERTO
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV1021-DDATAUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CPER-INV      TO COCV1021-DDATAUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV1021-DDATAUS-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       1001-VER-PERIODO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     1002-VER-FERIAS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1002-VER-FERIAS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1002-VER-FERIAS ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV1020-DDATAUS TO WS-DTMESANO.
      *
           INITIALIZE VIAL1000-AREA-COMUNICACAO.
           MOVE CON-99         TO VIAL1000-COD-PROCESSO.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO    TO VIATW300-DATA10.
           PERFORM VIATP300-CONV-DATA108
              THRU VIATP300-CONV-DATA108-EXIT.
           MOVE VIATW300-DATA8 TO VIAL1000-DAT-INPUT1.
           PERFORM VIAP1000-ROTINA-DATAS
              THRU VIAP1000-EXIT.

           IF    VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND ( VIAL1000-DAT-RES-SEM     EQUAL CON-S
           OR    VIAL1000-DAT-RES-SEM     EQUAL CON-D )
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV1021-DDATAUS-S
              MOVE COCK0001-DATAUS-FDS    TO COCV1021-DDATAUS-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV1021-DDATAUS-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       1002-VER-FERIAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1020-CIDEMP  TO COCD7601-CIDEMP.
           MOVE COCV1020-DDATAUS TO COCD7601-DDATAUS.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURCOT76
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT7601               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT76
               INTO
                   :COCD7601-CIDEMP
                 , :COCD7601-DDATAUS
                 , :COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO
                 , :COCD7601-NHORAS
                 , :COCD7601-CSITU
                 , :COCD7601-CUSERAPR
                 , :COCD7601-DDATAPR
                 , :COCD7601-CUSERID
                 , :COCD7601-HTIMEST
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7601 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL DB2-NOTFND
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           ADD 1 TO WS-CONTADOR.

           EVALUATE WS-CONTADOR
           WHEN 1 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO1
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS1
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU1
           WHEN 2 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO2
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS2
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU2
           WHEN 3 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO3
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS3
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU3
           WHEN 4 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO4
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS4
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU4
           WHEN 5 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO5
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS5
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU5
           WHEN 6 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO6
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS6
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU6
           WHEN 7 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO7
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS7
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU7
           WHEN 8 MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO TO COCV1021-NIDPROJECTO8
                  MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS      TO COCV1021-NHORAS8
                  MOVE COCD7601-CSITU       TO COCV1021-CSITU8
           END-EVALUATE.

           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.

       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT76
           END-EXEC.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1021-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV1021-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1021-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP1000.
           COPY VIATP300.
           COPY VIAP0016.
